name: Steven Pinker on Free Speech - Gold POSU

metadata.name: Free Speech is Fundamental - Gold
metadata.description: These Proof of Support (POSU) collectibles provide you access to intimate Zoom calls with Steven Pinker -  renowned Harvard Professor, best-selling author, and experimental psychologist - to discuss his views on the fundamental nature of free speech. These exclusive calls will happen 3 times per year for the next 4 years.
